    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. This example has had the critical VANOS system overhauled and the rod bearings replaced, addressing the primary failure points of the platform. Power is routed through a 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is preserved via proactive subframe reinforcement, and the suspension geometry is sharpened by Bilstein dampers and refreshed poly-bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains tight and the throttle response is exceptionally linear. A true driver\u2019s spec for those prioritizing mechanical health and visceral feedback.",
